{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1b8e55c20e","title":"杂文〈鸡翼下的鹰隼〉","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f774fb4ab4","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"1b8e55c20e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7991a1af47","name":"郭士英"},{"id":"ea25ac8f66","name":"西北农学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9422da552e","type":"title","text":"杂文〈鸡翼下的鹰隼〉","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1b8e55c20e"},{"id":"e5d31a3b3d","type":"authors","text":"西北农学院郭士英","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1b8e55c20e"},{"id":"6de9a04fd2","type":"paragraph","text":"历次的运动中都有一群“积极分子”，他们在党的指导下冲锋陷阵勇敢斗争，他们是运动的号角，人民的战士，他们是党孵育下的宝贝，培养对象、未来党员，他们是党鸡翼下的鹰隼。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1b8e55c20e"},{"id":"0361e958ec","type":"paragraph","text":"但是这次运动中却大大不同，鹰隼变成了娇嫩的鸡雏，他们大多沉默寡言，老成持重，他们也得不到培养和指导。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1b8e55c20e"},{"id":"af35648075","type":"appellation","text":"鹰隼们！假如你们真是人民的雄鹰，那么发挥你们历来的积极性，揭发一切污浊的东西，在这次运动中也作个急先锋。否则你们不过是可怜的鹰雏！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1b8e55c20e"},{"id":"25fbc5676c","type":"paragraph","text":" (植保系讲师  郭士英)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1b8e55c20e"},{"id":"a47c64f88e","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1b8e55c20e"}],"page":{"id":"67bd7405f9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1b8e55c20e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}